Popular Nollywood actor Ifeanyi Ezeokeke popularly known as Ugo Shave Me in conspiracy 1&2 has been down with an unknown and strange illness. Ifeanyi was visited by notable Nollywood veterans, Ipechukwu Diewait and Ejike Okoye. The stars who paid him visit said the illness is strange when asked the nature of his illness. See Photo: Source